casebody.data:
EDDIE KELLY v. STATE OF FLORIDA 16 So. (2nd) 344

January Term, 1944

January 25, 1944 Division A J. M. & H. P. Sapp, and Whit Newberry, for appellant. J. Tom Watson, Attorney General, John C. Wynn and Bourke Floyd, Special Assistant Attorney General, for ap-pellee. PER CURIAM:

The record in this case having been duly considered and no reversible error appearing, the judgment is affirmed.

BUFORD, C. J., TERRELL, CHAPMAN and ADAMS, JJ., concur.
